================================================================================
  SECTION 7 — ARCHITECTURE NOTES
================================================================================

  Service Placement Inconsistency:
    8 service interfaces defined in Core/Interfaces/ have their implementations
    in Infrastructure/Services/ instead of Core/Services/. Business logic
    should live in Core; only data-access/integration code in Infrastructure.
    Affected: MentionService, RecommendationService, OfferService,
    CollectionService, DonationService, SnippetService, IntegrationService,
    RedirectService.

  Missing Database Indexes (based on query patterns):
    - PostsTags.TagId (for tag-based post queries)
    - MembersNewsletters (MemberId, NewsletterId) UNIQUE constraint
    - EmailRecipients.EmailId (for recipients-by-email queries)
    - MembersLabels (MemberId, LabelId) UNIQUE constraint
    - Suppressions.Email (for is-suppressed lookups)

  ContentService Tag Update Inefficiency:
    File: src/HowToSoftware.Core/Services/ContentService.cs (lines 131-145)
    PostsTags.Clear() loads the entire collection then deletes one-by-one.
    For posts with many tags, use ExecuteDeleteAsync directly.


